data.description: Perched on a serene one-acre lot, this meticulously maintained 3-bed, 2.5-bath home showcases captivating views of the Olympic Mountains and Hood Canal. Its open concept layout boasts hardwood floors, a gourmet kitchen with double ovens and granite slab counters, and an elegant crown molding touch. Enjoy cozy evenings by the river rock fireplace with hidden TV storage, while the main floor master suite offers a five-piece master bath with a soaking tub and walk-in shower. The property also features a 2-car garage with a bonus room, kitchen space, and a 3/4 bath, making it a truly exceptional retreat.
